      <h2>PCIN KIT Cards</h2>
      <p>PCIN and Huron County Library system have partnered with the Avon   Maitland District School Board in a pilot project which will putÂ­ a   public library card in the hands of every student. Â­A library card willÂ­   arm Â­students with a reliable source of information while also hoping   to build literacy skills and promote a love of reading. Â­All students   from kindergarten to grade 12 will be given a library registration form   which, once completed, will provide them with a card to access all of   the libraries' resources.</p>
      <p>Check out the link below for more information!</p>
